      "role": "user",
      "content": "i had the weirdest thing happen today and im actually kind of spooked. i was looking at this old copper keychain on my desk this morning and i kept seeing this weird flickering effect, like a shadow of it moving before i even touched it. then literally an hour later, the news breaks about that massive pileup on the i95 freeway. it felt like i saw the impact happening in the reflection of the metal before it actually happened. has anyone else ever felt like they were seeing things \"before\" they actually occur? like a temporal echo or something?",
